    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buildings that house healthcare facilities for outpatient care, often where patients receive treatment at reduced fees. The term also refers to facilities or hospital departments devoted to a particular group of diseases, such as a psychiatric clinic, neurology clinic, or surgery clinic, whether or not fees are reduced.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000093795/Encyclopedia Britannica Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>提供門診服務的健康設施所在建築，病人診療費用較為低廉。此詞彙亦指稱負責專門疾病科別的設施或醫院部門，諸如精神科診所、神經科診所或外科診所等，診療費用則視情況而減免。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Edifícios que abrigam instalações de saúde para atendimento ambulatorial, geralmente onde os pacientes recebem tratamento a preços reduzidos. O termo também se refere a instalações ou departamentos de hospitais dedicados a um determinado grupo de doenças, como uma clínica psiquiátrica, clínica de neurologia ou clínica cirúrgica, independentemente de as taxas serem reduzidas ou não.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000316/CVAA-BR</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
